#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "<color_light_red>Secronom+ Lore Expansion</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>Secronom+ 背景扩展</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_light_red>Secronom+ Lore Expansion</color>
#: .\modinfo.json
