#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_BOWs.json
msgid "bio-organic sword"
msgid_plural "bio-organic swords"
msgstr[0] "生物有机剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bio-organic sword'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A large bio-organic weapon with a sharp, calcified edge and hilt consisting "
"of membranous vein webbings."
msgstr "一把大型生物有机武器，拥有锋利的钙化刃缘，剑柄由膜状静脉网构成。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_BOWs.json
msgid "bio-organic sword<color_light_green>+</color>"
msgid_plural "bio-organic swords<color_light_green>+</color>"
msgstr[0] "生物有机剑<color_light_green>+</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bio-organic sword<color_light_green>+</color>',
#. 'str_pl': 'bio-organic swords<color_light_green>+</color>'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A large bio-organic weapon with a sharp, calcified edge and hilt consisting of membranous vein webbings.\n"
"\n"
"It has <color_light_green>core</color> (blade zombie) in its mod slot, providing:\n"
"<color_white>Cutting damage: <color_light_green>+30%</color></color>"
msgstr ""
"一把大型生物有机武器，拥有锋利的钙化刃缘，剑柄由膜状静脉网构成。\n"
"\n"
"其模组槽中装有<color_light_green>核心</color>（刃锋僵尸），提供：\n"
"<color_white>切割伤害：<color_light_green>+30%</color></color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bio-organic sword<color_light_green>+</color>',
#. 'str_pl': 'bio-organic swords<color_light_green>+</color>'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A large bio-organic weapon with a sharp, calcified edge and hilt consisting of membranous vein webbings.\n"
"\n"
"It has <color_light_green>core</color> (tendril zombie) in its mod slot, providing:\n"
"<color_white>* Bonus on-hit attacks.</color>"
msgstr ""
"一把大型生物有机武器，拥有锋利的钙化刃缘，剑柄由膜状静脉网构成。\n"
"\n"
"其模组槽中装有<color_light_green>核心</color>（触须僵尸），提供：\n"
"<color_white>* 命中时附加额外攻击。</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
#: Files\Items\-Essentials\secro_ammo_types.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "flesh"
msgid_plural "flesh"
msgstr[0] "血肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh', 'str_pl': 'flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"A throbbing, seemingly alive slab of meat. Not edible for you to eat, but it"
" is a necessary catalyst for flesh weaving and as a \"fuel\" for bio-"
"organics."
msgstr "一块搏动、看似活着的肉块。对你来说不可食用，但它是血肉编织的必要催化剂，并可作为生物有机体的\"燃料\"。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid "chunk of flesh"
msgid_plural "chunk of flesh"
msgstr[0] "肉块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chunk of flesh', 'str_pl': 'chunk of flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"A big throbbing, seemingly alive slab of meat. Not edible for you to eat, "
"but it is a necessary catalyst for flesh weaving and as a \"fuel\" for bio-"
"organics."
msgstr "一大块搏动、看似活着的肉块。对你来说不可食用，但它是血肉编织的必要催化剂，并可作为生物有机体的\"燃料\"。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid "<color_light_blue>gunner creation</color> - bone needle"
msgid_plural "<color_light_blue>gunner creation</color> - bone needles"
msgstr[0] "<color_light_blue>枪手造物</color> - 骨针"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '<color_light_blue>gunner creation</color> - bone
#. needle'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"Formed using the flesh's versatile cell reconstruction. This bio-organic "
"needle is tipped with a sharp end that can easily pierce through flesh and "
"mildly-armoured targets."
msgstr "利用血肉的多功能细胞重构形成。这种生物有机针尖端锋利，能轻易刺穿血肉和轻度装甲目标。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid "flesh pouch"
msgid_plural "flesh pouchs"
msgstr[0] "血肉囊袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh pouch'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"A small orifice with small residue for storage. Usually located on small "
"bio-organic devices."
msgstr "带有小型残留物用于储存的小型孔口。通常位于小型生物有机装置上。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid "flesh residue"
msgid_plural "flesh residues"
msgstr[0] "血肉残留物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh residue'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"A some sort of pouched orifice that consumes a special type of flesh. "
"Unifies permanently to a flesh vessel."
msgstr "一种囊状孔口，消耗特殊类型的血肉。永久性地与某个血肉容器融合。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid "massive flesh residue"
msgid_plural "massive flesh residues"
msgstr[0] "巨型血肉残留物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'massive flesh residue'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"A massive pouched orifice that consumes a special type of flesh. Unifies "
"permanently to a certain flesh vessel."
msgstr "一个巨大的囊状孔口，消耗特殊类型的血肉。永久性地与某个特定的血肉容器融合。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid "Secronom module UPS"
msgid_plural "Secronom module UPS"
msgstr[0] "Secronom模块UPS"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Secronom module UPS', 'str_pl': 'Secronom module
#. UPS'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"A UPS with an extremely high-capacity battery specially designed to be used "
"for all Secronom module implant types."
msgstr "一种配备极高容量电池的UPS，专为所有Secronom模块植入类型设计。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid "SP experimental battery"
msgid_plural "SP experimental batteries"
msgstr[0] "SP实验电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'SP experimental battery', 'str_pl': 'SP
#. experimental batteries'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"A light, but high-capacity battery cell, for use with certain power armor "
"modules."
msgstr "一种轻量但高容量的电池单元，用于某些动力装甲模块。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid "overcharged lump of flesh"
msgid_plural "overcharged lump of fleshs"
msgstr[0] "过载血肉块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'overcharged lump of flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_ammo_mags.json
msgid ""
"This large lump of organic material stores incredibly high amount of energy "
"produced by an artificial flesh core. Mainly used to power up a certain mech"
" suit."
msgstr "这块大型有机材料储存着由人造血肉核心产生的惊人能量。主要用于为某种机甲套装供能。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_books.json
msgid "Secronom Project \"Flesh\": Research Results"
msgid_plural "copies of Secronom Project \"Flesh\": Research Results"
msgstr[0] "Secronom项目“血肉”：研究成果"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Secronom Project "Flesh": Research Results',
#. 'str_pl': 'copies of Secronom Project "Flesh": Research Results'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_books.json
msgid ""
"This binder of highly technical papers describe the recent findings to "
"multiple tests involving the flesh.  It's stamped \"APPROVED\"…"
msgstr "这本高度技术性的论文夹描述了近期对血肉进行的多项测试的发现。上面盖有“批准”印章…"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_books.json
msgid "Secronom Project \"Flesh\": Field Research"
msgid_plural "copies of Secronom Project \"Flesh\": Field Research"
msgstr[0] "Secronom项目“血肉”：实地研究"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Secronom Project "Flesh": Field Research',
#. 'str_pl': 'copies of Secronom Project "Flesh": Field Research'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_books.json
msgid ""
"This binder of highly technical papers describe the wearer's protocol in "
"wearing the bio-organic power armor, with a simple demonstration in forming "
"its \"food\"."
msgstr "这本高度技术性的论文夹描述了穿戴者穿着生物有机动力装甲的协议，并简单演示了如何形成其“食物”。"

