#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_flesh.json
msgid "bio-organic flesh"
msgid_plural "bio-organic fleshs"
msgstr[0] "生物有机血肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bio-organic flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_flesh.json
msgid ""
"A chunk of heavily compressed flesh. Rubbery yet stiff, its toughness is "
"compared to that of kevlar."
msgstr "一大块高度压缩的血肉。富有弹性却又坚硬，其韧性堪比凯夫拉纤维。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_flesh.json
msgid "molten flesh vessel"
msgid_plural "molten flesh vessels"
msgstr[0] "熔融血肉容器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'molten flesh vessel'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_flesh.json
msgid ""
"A bio-organic exoskeleton turned into a mish-mash of flesh and bones. "
"Completely unusable in its form."
msgstr "一个生物有机外骨骼变成了血肉与骨骼的混合物。以其当前形态完全无法使用。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_fleshcamp_marks.json
