#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"A small pouch that can be used to store most types of small ammunition; "
"rockets, however, will not fit.  Use insert to store ammunition."
msgstr "一个小型袋子，可用于存放大多数类型的小型弹药；但火箭弹无法放入。使用插入操作来存放弹药。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "ammo satchel"
