msgid "Stash ammo"
msgstr "藏匿弹药"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ammo satchel'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"A fleshy ammo bag worn at the waist.  It is capable of holding a single "
"large magazine or speedloader close at hand."
msgstr "一种系在腰间的肉质弹药袋。它能容纳一个大型弹匣或快速装弹器，便于随时取用。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "chest ammo pouch"
msgid_plural "chest ammo pouches"
msgstr[0] "胸前弹药袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chest ammo pouch', 'str_pl': 'chest ammo
#. pouches'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"A fleshy ammo pouch that can be strapped to your chest and hold a single "
"magazine or speedloader close at hand."
msgstr "一种肉质弹药袋，可绑在胸前，容纳一个弹匣或快速装弹器，便于随时取用。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "chest rig"
msgid_plural "chest rigs"
msgstr[0] "胸挂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chest rig'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"Popularized during the Vietnam War, chest rigs like these are typically "
"plain, barebones affairs consisting of three or more pouches in a row, with "
"straps to secure them on your chest.  This one can hold four magazines or "
"speedloaders in its pouches."
msgstr ""
"这类胸挂在越南战争期间流行起来，通常是朴素、基础的设计，包含一排三个或更多袋子，配有绑带固定在胸前。这个胸挂的袋子可容纳四个弹匣或快速装弹器。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "XL chest rig"
msgid_plural "XL chest rigs"
msgstr[0] "XL胸挂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chest rig'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"Popularized during the Vietnam War, chest rigs like these are typically "
"plain, barebones affairs consisting of three or more pouches in a row, with "
"straps to secure them on your chest.  This one can hold four magazines or "
"speedloaders in its pouches and fits larger-than-human forms."
msgstr ""
"这类胸挂袋在越南战争期间开始流行，通常是朴素、基础的设计，由三个或更多并排的弹匣袋组成，配有绑带固定在胸前。这款胸挂袋的弹匣袋可容纳四个弹匣或快速装弹器，且适合比人类体型更大的形态。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "javelin bag"
msgid_plural "javelin bags"
msgstr[0] "标枪袋"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'javelin bag'}.
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "Stash javelins"
msgstr "存放标枪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'javelin bag'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"An open medieval-looking bag, designed to store javelins within easy reach."
msgstr "一个敞开的中世纪风格袋子，设计用于存放标枪，便于取用。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "ankle ammo pouch"
msgid_plural "ankle ammo pouches"
msgstr[0] "脚踝弹药袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ankle ammo pouch', 'str_pl': 'ankle ammo
#. pouches'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"A small fleshy ammo pouch that can be strapped to your ankle and hold a "
"single small magazine or speedloader close at hand."
msgstr "一个小型肉质弹药袋，可绑在脚踝上，随身携带一个小型弹匣或快速装弹器。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "leg ammo pouch"
msgid_plural "leg ammo pouches"
msgstr[0] "腿部弹药袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'leg ammo pouch', 'str_pl': 'leg ammo pouches'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"A fleshy ammo pouch that can be strapped to your leg and hold two magazines "
"or speedloaders close at hand."
msgstr "一个肉质弹药袋，可绑在腿上，随身携带两个弹匣或快速装弹器。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "quiver"
msgid_plural "quivers"
msgstr[0] "箭袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'quiver'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"A fleshy quiver worn at the waist that can hold 20 arrows or bolts.  Use "
"insert to store arrows or bolts."
msgstr "一个系在腰间的肉质箭袋，可容纳20支箭或弩箭。使用插入功能来存放箭或弩箭。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "large quiver"
msgid_plural "large quivers"
msgstr[0] "大型箭袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large quiver'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"A large fleshy quiver worn on the back, that can hold 60 arrows or bolts.  "
"Historically used by horse archers, rather than foot archers, but neither of"
" THEM had to fight zombies.  Use insert to store arrows or bolts."
msgstr "一个背在背上的大型肉质箭袋，可容纳60支箭或弩箭。历史上多由骑射手使用，而非步弓手，但两者都无需对抗僵尸。使用插入功能来存放箭或弩箭。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "tac vest"
msgid_plural "tac vests"
msgstr[0] "战术背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tac vest'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"This light vest is meant to carry your gear and ammunition comfortably "
"distributed about your torso.  They are popular amongst law enforcement, but"
" less so than combination tactical vests incorporating Kevlar.  Lightweight "
"and easy to don, this vest can hold four magazines close at hand in its many"
" pouches."
msgstr ""
"这款轻型背心旨在将装备和弹药舒适地分布在躯干上。它们在执法部门中很受欢迎，但不如结合了凯夫拉材质的组合战术背心。轻便易穿，这款背心的多个弹匣袋可随身携带四个弹匣。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid "XL tac vest"
msgid_plural "XL tac vests"
msgstr[0] "加大战术背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL tac vest'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_ammo_pouch.json
msgid ""
"This light vest is meant to carry your gear and ammunition comfortably "
"distributed about your torso.  They are popular amongst law enforcement, but"
" less so than combination tactical vests incorporating Kevlar.  Oversized "
"and easy to don, this vest can hold four magazines close at hand in its many"
" pouches."
msgstr ""
"这款轻型背心旨在将装备和弹药舒适地分布在躯干上。它们在执法部门中很受欢迎，但不如结合了凯夫拉材质的组合战术背心。超大尺寸且易于穿戴，这款背心的多个弹匣袋可随身携带四个弹匣。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_cloak.json
msgid "cloak"
msgid_plural "cloaks"
msgstr[0] "斗篷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cloak'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_cloak.json
msgid "A heavy cloak meant to be thrown over your body."
msgstr "一件厚重的斗篷，设计用于披在身上。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_holster.json
msgid "back holster"
msgid_plural "back holsters"
msgstr[0] "背部枪套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'back holster'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_holster.json
msgid ""
"A holster, big enough for a rifle or other large gun.  Designed to be "
"strapped to the back.  Whilst initially cumbersome it becomes much easier to"
" use with practice.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr "一个足够容纳步枪或其他大型枪支的枪套，设计用于绑在背部。虽然最初使用起来有些笨拙，但通过练习会变得容易得多。激活以收枪或拔枪。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_holster.json
msgid "baldric holster"
msgid_plural "baldric holsters"
msgstr[0] "肩带式枪套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'baldric holster'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_holster.json
msgid ""
"A harness which can hold up to six pistol-sized guns in total, available for"
" quick drawing.  Historically similar harnesses were used by pirates to "
"carry multiple loaded flintlock pistols at once, as reloading them is a "
"lengthy process.  Activate to holster/draw a gun."
msgstr ""
"一种可容纳最多六把手枪尺寸枪支的背带，便于快速拔枪。历史上，海盗曾使用类似的背带同时携带多把已装填的燧发手枪，因为重新装填过程耗时较长。激活以收枪/拔枪。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\Armors\secro_holster.json
msgid "ankle holster"
msgid_plural "ankle holsters"
msgstr[0] "脚踝枪套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ankle holster'}
