msgstr "肉质床铺"

#. ~ Description for flesh bed
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"A lump of flesh carefully molded into a bed. Although it may be sticky, "
"it'll keep you warm."
msgstr "一块精心塑造成床铺的肉块。虽然可能有些黏腻，但能保暖。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "floor residue"
msgstr "地面残留物"

#. ~ Description for floor residue
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"A gaping mouth on the floor. Good for storing items, just don't fall into "
"it."
msgstr "地面上一个张开的嘴巴。适合存放物品，只是别掉进去。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "residue"
msgstr "残留物"

#. ~ Description for residue
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid ""
"A gaping mouth protruding from the floor. Great for storing items, just "
"don't go inside it."
msgstr "一张从地面突出的血盆大口。非常适合存放物品，只是别走进去。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
msgid "flesh rack"
msgstr "血肉货架"

#. ~ Description for flesh rack
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn_camp.json
