#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid "SPEMF bone launcher"
msgid_plural "SPEMF bone launchers"
msgstr[0] "SPEMF骨刺发射器"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This is a rather vague integral weapon system for the Secronom Project's "
"Experimental Mech \"Flesh\". Possesses wide variety of bio-organic guns to "
"shoot different projectiles which consumes flesh as ammunition. Mech's hand "
"have currently turned into a bone launcher, which volleys bone spikes at a "
"high rate."
msgstr ""
"这是塞克洛诺姆计划实验机甲“血肉”的一套相当模糊的集成武器系统。拥有多种生物有机枪械，可发射不同弹体，并以血肉作为弹药消耗。机甲的手部目前已转变为骨刺发射器，能够高速连发骨刺。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid "high auto"
msgstr "高速全自动"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid "SPEMF bone cannon"
msgid_plural "SPEMF bone cannons"
msgstr[0] "SPEMF骨炮"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid ""
"Morphs the mech's hands into bone cannons which launches and sprays bone "
"spikes. Consumes chunks of flesh."
msgstr "将机甲双手变形为骨炮，可发射并喷洒骨刺。消耗肉块。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid "SPEMF gun morphs"
msgstr "SPEMF枪械变形"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "secro_fleshmech_gun_spikes"
msgstr "secro_fleshmech_gun_spikes"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid "SPEMF acid launcher"
msgid_plural "SPEMF acid launchers"
msgstr[0] "SPEMF酸液发射器"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid ""
"Morphs the mech's hands into heavy acid launchers, allowing one to spray "
"large amounts of blood acid. Consumes chunks of flesh."
msgstr "将机甲双手变形为重酸液发射器，可喷洒大量血液酸液。消耗肉块。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid "SPEMF acid spitter"
msgid_plural "SPEMF acid spitters"
msgstr[0] "SPEMF酸液喷射器"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A large, elongated limb-like proboscis that sprouts from the back of the "
"mech when activated. Bursts globs of blood acid."
msgstr "激活时从机甲背部伸出的细长肢状口器。可爆裂出血液酸液团。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_mech_weapons.json
msgid "SPEMF accessories"
msgstr "SPEMF配件"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
#: Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets_modded.json
msgid "laser beam turret"
msgid_plural "laser beam turrets"
msgstr[0] "激光炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'laser beam turret'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid ""
"SDP-L1, also known as Secronom Defense Project Type \"Laser\", is an "
"advanced laser turret based from the miniature TX-5LR Cerberus. Its "
"autonomous laser cannon fires a concentrated beam of pure heat that pierces "
"through targets. Every shot requires an immensive power from its source."
msgstr ""
"SDP-L1，也称为塞克诺防御计划“激光”型，是一种基于微型TX-5LR "
"Cerberus的先进激光炮塔。其自主激光炮发射一道集中的纯热光束，穿透目标。每次射击都需要其能源提供巨大功率。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'laser beam turret'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
#: Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets_modded.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s shoots a ray of heat at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s向%3$s射出一道热射线！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid "electroshock turret"
msgid_plural "electroshock turrets"
msgstr[0] "电击炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'electroshock turret'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid ""
"SDP-E3, a highly modified turret developed for immobilizing nearby creatures"
" with the use of its electrifying tesla-coil. Its 360 degree AI sensor cam "
"allows it to identify foes and discharge the turret automatically. Firmly "
"embedded to the terrain, it requires a huge amount of power from its source "
"to operate."
msgstr ""
"SDP-E3，一种经过高度改装的炮塔，旨在利用其带电的特斯拉线圈使附近的生物无法动弹。其360度AI传感器摄像头可识别敌人并自动发射炮塔。它牢固地嵌入地形中，需要从电源获取大量电力才能运作。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'electroshock turret'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s sends an electric current!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s释放了一道电流！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid "graviton turret"
msgid_plural "graviton turrets"
msgstr[0] "引力子炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'graviton turret'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid ""
"SDP-G7P, a small turret that disorient movements of its target using strong "
"magnetic fields that is generated under its large, gaping barrel. The turret"
" is slow to recharge and the generated field doesn't last long, as it is a "
"prototype version of its predecessor."
msgstr ""
"SDP-G7P，一种小型炮塔，利用其巨大、敞开的炮管下生成的强磁场扰乱目标的行动。该炮塔充电缓慢，生成的磁场持续时间不长，因为它是其前代的原型版本。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'graviton turret'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_magenta>%1$s generates a energized field under %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>%1$s在%3$s下方生成了一个充能场！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'laser beam turret'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets_modded.json
msgid ""
"SDP-L1, also known as Secronom Defense Project Type \"Laser\", is an "
"advanced laser turret based from the miniature TX-5LR Cerberus. Its "
"autonomous laser cannon fires a concentrated beam of pure heat that pierces "
"through targets. It uses a modified storage battery that allows the turret "
"to operate on its own."
msgstr ""
"SDP-L1，又称Secronom防御计划“激光”型，是一种基于微型TX-5LR "
"Cerberus的先进激光炮塔。其自主激光炮发射一道集中的纯热光束，可穿透目标。它使用改良的蓄电池，使炮塔能够独立运作。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
msgid "vessel experimental"
msgid_plural "vessel experimentals"
msgstr[0] "实验型容器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vessel experimental'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
msgid ""
"A human who fell and succumbed to the flesh vessel exoskeleton - an "
"experimental battle suit developed by the Secronom Project. It has "
"completely fused with the body, and seem to have full control over it."
msgstr "一个倒下并屈服于血肉容器外骨骼的人类——这是Secronom项目开发的实验性战斗服。它已与身体完全融合，似乎能完全控制宿主。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vessel experimental'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_magenta>%1$s aims at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>%1$s 瞄准了 %3$s！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vessel experimental'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
msgid ""
"A human who fell and succumbed to the flesh vessel exoskeleton - an "
"experimental battle suit developed by the Secronom Project - and by the "
"looks of it, the body has been recently devoured. Strands of flesh writhe "
"incessantly around it."
msgstr ""
"一个倒下并屈服于血肉容器外骨骼的人类——这是Secronom项目开发的实验性战斗服——从外观判断，其身体最近刚被吞噬。血肉细丝在周围不停地扭动。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vessel experimental'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_magenta>A gunner armament emerges from %1$s's body, aiming at "
"%3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>一门枪械武装从 %1$s 体内浮现，瞄准了 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_mech.json
msgid "SP Experimental Mech \"Flesh\""
msgid_plural "SP Experimental Mech \"Flesh\"s"
msgstr[0] "SP实验机甲“血肉”"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'SP Experimental Mech "Flesh"'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_mech.json
msgid ""
"This experimental mech type \"Flesh\" is the most recent (and last) mechsuit"
" produced by the engineers of the Secronom Project. Very scarce and limited "
"to military use only, it was designed to take on the main force of the "
"battlefield thanks to its exotic yet nigh indestructible material, "
"especially supplemented with a variety of gun morphs. Unfortunately, it "
"requires one to wear a bio-organic power and link it with the mech to accept"
" you as its rider."
msgstr ""
"这款实验型机甲“血肉”是Secronom项目工程师制造的最新（也是最后）的机甲服。数量极为稀少且仅限于军事用途，它被设计用于应对战场主力，这得益于其奇特且近乎坚不可摧的材料，特别是辅以多种枪械变形能力。不幸的是，它需要穿戴者配备生物有机动力装置，并将其与机甲链接以接受你作为骑手。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'SP Experimental Mech "Flesh"'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_mech.json
msgid ""
"This experimental mech type \"Flesh\" is the most recent (and last) mechsuit"
" produced by the engineers of the Secronom Project. Very scarce and limited "
"to military use only, it was designed to take on the main force of the "
"battlefield thanks to its exotic yet nigh indestructible material, "
"especially supplemented with a variety of gun morphs."
msgstr ""
"这款实验型机甲“血肉”是Secronom项目工程师制造的最新（也是最后）的机甲服。数量极为稀少且仅限于军事用途，它被设计用于应对战场主力，这得益于其奇特且近乎坚不可摧的材料，特别是辅以多种枪械变形能力。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_mission_items.json
msgid "desaturated resin"
msgid_plural "desaturated resins"
msgstr[0] "褪色树脂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'desaturated resin'}
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_mission_items.json
msgid "A chunk of thick, charred resin."
msgstr "一块厚重、焦黑的树脂。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_mission_items.json
msgid "SS sampler kit - enigma"
msgid_plural "SS sampler kit - enigmas"
msgstr[0] "SS采样套件 - 谜团"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'SS sampler kit - enigma'}
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_mission_items.json
msgid ""
"A small, chip-like device with a built-in scanner that checks for \"enigma\""
" specimens. Activate to scan and obtain a sample from the target."
msgstr "一种内置扫描器的小型芯片状设备，用于检测“谜团”样本。激活后可扫描目标并获取样本。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'a spell'}'
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_mission_items.json
msgid ""
"<color_dark_gray>The sampler kit starts to scan...\n"
"<color_light_green>The sampler kit shreds the shapeshifter!"
msgstr ""
"<color_dark_gray>采样套件开始扫描...\n"
"<color_light_green>采样套件撕碎了变形体！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Collect'}
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_mission_items.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by an item. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Provides a desaturated resin.'"
msgstr ""
"物品施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读：\n"
"‘提供一块褪色树脂。’"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Reach the BOW Chamber"
msgstr "抵达BOW实验室"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "…"
msgstr "……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"You've heard the plan. Ask the other survivors for our short, bloody travel "
"once you have accepted my request."
msgstr "你已经知晓计划。接受我的请求后，向其他幸存者询问我们短暂而血腥的行程。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Good. Now go, we can't waste time in our current situation."
msgstr "很好。现在出发吧，我们当前的处境不容浪费时间。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Well then... Lets talk about it again later."
msgstr "那么……我们稍后再谈此事。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Those specimens are nasty in close range."
msgstr "那些样本在近距离非常棘手。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "We've got to get going."
msgstr "我们得继续前进了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Thank you. Now we've got more spaces to move around. That being said, tell "
"the others to stay put in this area... they also need your assistance."
msgstr "谢谢。现在我们有了更多活动空间。话虽如此，告诉其他人留在这个区域……他们也需要你的帮助。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Gather materials for SDP-L1 turret"
msgstr "收集SDP-L1炮塔的材料"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Gather materials for SDP-L1 turret'}'
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Collect <color_light_green>4 chunks of steel</color>, <color_light_green>18 "
"scrap metals</color>, <color_light_green>9 electronic scraps</color>, "
"<color_light_green>9 power converters</color>, <color_light_green>5 copper "
"wires</color> and <color_light_green>a broken laser beam turret</color>."
msgstr ""
"收集<color_light_green>4块钢锭</color>、<color_light_green>18个金属废料</color>、<color_light_green>9个电子废料</color>、<color_light_green>9个电源转换器</color>、<color_light_green>5根铜线</color>和<color_light_green>一个损坏的激光束炮塔</color>。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"I'd like you to retrieve a broken SDP-L1 from the bunker and other essential"
" parts for me to fully repair the turret."
msgstr "我希望你从掩体中取回一个损坏的SDP-L1以及其他必要零件，以便我完全修复炮塔。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Then go, give them all to me afterwards."
msgstr "然后去吧，之后把所有东西都交给我。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "If it's too heavy, haul it."
msgstr "如果太重，就拖过来。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Good. The process may take an hour. While I'm repairing it, you should talk "
"to others if they need your assistance."
msgstr "很好。这个过程可能需要一个小时。在我修复期间，你应该问问其他人是否需要帮助。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Clear the enigma chamber"
msgstr "清理谜团密室"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"So she wants you to clear out the enigma chamber, and you need my help to "
"access that room. But are you ready? You can refuse if it felt like a "
"deathwish."
msgstr "所以她想要你清理谜团密室，而你需要我的帮助才能进入那个房间。但你准备好了吗？如果感觉像送死，你可以拒绝。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Let's head to that chamber real quick!"
msgstr "我们快去那个密室吧！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Just ask me again once you're ready to take on."
msgstr "等你准备好接手时再问我一次。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Since this facility have come into chaos, we might see creatures other than "
"them."
msgstr "自从这个设施陷入混乱以来，我们可能会看到除了它们之外的其他生物。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Did you killed them?"
msgstr "你干掉它们了吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Great! Lets head back to others and see if they need anything else. Enigma "
"chamber is pretty messed up anyway."
msgstr "太好了！我们回去找其他人，看看他们是否还需要什么。反正谜团密室已经一团糟了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Really? I've come alongside you and yet you lied to something you obviously "
"didn't do?"
msgstr "真的吗？我一直跟你在一起，你却对明明没做的事撒谎？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Obtain a sample from the shapeshifter"
msgstr "从变形者身上获取样本"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Obtain a sample from the
#. shapeshifter'}'
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Collect a <color_light_green>desaturated resin</color> from a "
"<color_light_red>shapeshifter</color>. Use the tool provided to obtain the "
"required item then bring it back once you've complete the task."
msgstr ""
"从<color_light_red>变形者</color>身上收集一份<color_light_green>脱饱和树脂</color>。使用提供的工具获取所需物品，完成任务后带回。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"You must obtain a sample from that creature using a sampler kit I'm about to"
" provide once you're ready."
msgstr "你必须使用我即将提供的采样工具包从那个生物身上获取样本，等你准备好。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Okay, here's the kit. It is set to scan for an enigma specimen. I've sent "
"the coordinates to our guard and talk to him about this, he'll show you the "
"way. But remember, this creature uses deception to hide itself."
msgstr "好的，这是工具包。它已设置为扫描谜团样本。我已将坐标发送给我们的守卫，跟他谈谈这个，他会给你指路。但记住，这种生物会使用欺骗手段隐藏自己。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Be cautious on using the sampler kit, as it scans only the enigma, otherwise"
" you'll waste batteries."
msgstr "使用采样工具包时要小心，因为它只扫描谜团生物，否则你会浪费电池。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "How's the sample?"
msgstr "样本怎么样？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Well done, survivor. I'll start to identify this resin, and hope it can of "
"good use."
msgstr "干得好，幸存者。我会开始鉴定这种树脂，希望它能派上用场。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Slay the shapeshifter?"
msgstr "击杀变形者？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"She gave me the coordinates as soon as the drone reported her. I'll help you"
" out collecting the sample, and fend off this creature from you. So, are you"
" ready?"
msgstr "无人机一报告她的位置，她就给了我坐标。我会帮你收集样本，并帮你抵挡这个生物。那么，你准备好了吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Good. The target is not far from here."
msgstr "很好。目标离这里不远。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "I never encountered this creature..."
msgstr "我从未遇到过这种生物……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Wait. It's not the right one... I guess we lost it."
msgstr "等等。这不是我们要找的那个……我想我们跟丢了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Feed your flesh"
msgstr "喂养你的血肉"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Feed your flesh'}'
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"\"Feed\" the bio-organic exoskeleton by activating <color_light_blue>Feed</color> command under the spellcasting tab (undefined by default). Alternatively, you can activate the <color_yellow>Metabolic Distribution</color> bionic, but it is advisable to use it only if you ran out of flesh.\n"
"\n"
"To complete this mission, obtain a <color_light_green>blob glob</color>. It's the main ingredient in creating food for your suit."
msgstr ""
"通过激活施法标签下的<color_light_blue>喂养</color>命令（默认未定义）来“喂养”生物有机外骨骼。或者，你可以激活<color_yellow>代谢分配</color>仿生体，但建议仅在血肉耗尽时使用。\n"
"\n"
"要完成此任务，获取一个<color_light_green>粘液团块</color>。它是为你的套装制造食物的主要成分。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npc_classes_facs.json
msgid "Secronom Researchers"
msgstr "塞克诺姆研究员"

#. ~ Description for Secronom Researchers
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npc_classes_facs.json
msgid ""
"A small group of scientists working under a certain project. Their advanced "
"development of utilities is their fortitude for survival."
msgstr "在某个项目下工作的一小群科学家。他们先进的实用工具开发是他们生存的支柱。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npc_classes_facs.json
#: Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Flesh"
msgstr "血肉"

#. ~ Description for Flesh
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npc_classes_facs.json
msgid ""
"A uniformed groups of humans/monsters created by the Secronom Project. They "
"rarely appear in the world, and is motivated to dominate the world."
msgstr "由塞克诺姆项目创造的统一着装的人类/怪物群体。他们很少在世界上出现，并以统治世界为动机。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npc_classes_facs.json
msgid "Secronom Scientist"
msgstr "塞克诺姆科学家"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npc_classes_facs.json
msgid "I'm one of the mfs who made secronom and shit."
msgstr "我就是搞出塞克诺姆这些破事的人之一。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npcs.json
msgid "scientist"
msgstr "科学家"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npcs.json
msgid "researcher"
msgstr "研究员"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_npcs.json
msgid "guard"
msgstr "守卫"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\+Essentials\secro_dialogue_effects.json
msgid "Some tendrils came off of the flesh after its relocation!"
msgstr "一些触须在血肉转移后脱落了！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr "你想要什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid ""
"We seem to find nothing...\n"
"We should go back."
msgstr ""
"我们似乎什么都没找到……\n"
"我们应该回去了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "You need something, survivor?"
msgstr "你需要什么吗，幸存者？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "We've got to go to the enigma chamber."
msgstr "我们得去谜题密室。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "What is it, survivor?"
msgstr "怎么了，幸存者？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "You're skilled more than what I've expected from you. Good job!"
msgstr "你的技能比我对你的预期还要出色。干得好！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Focus on our path! There's no time for chit-chats!"
msgstr "集中注意力在我们的路线上！没时间闲聊了！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "I heard it. We will protect these people from the mutant hordes."
msgstr "我听说了。我们会保护这些人免受突变体群的侵袭。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "You are not suppose to be in here, survivor."
msgstr "你不该在这里的，幸存者。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Okay. Follow my lead."
msgstr "好的。跟着我走。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "I know, now stand still and be a real guard."
msgstr "我知道，现在站好，做个真正的守卫。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "No, you're staying here."
msgstr "不，你得留在这里。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Do you need help?"
msgstr "你需要帮助吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "I need to go to enigma chamber."
msgstr "我需要去谜题密室。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "We're here now."
msgstr "我们现在到了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "About the coordinates..."
msgstr "关于坐标……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "We're here..."
msgstr "我们到了……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Okay then..."
msgstr "好吧，那么……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Nothing..."
msgstr "没什么……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "We better go..."
msgstr "我们最好走吧……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Nope. Bye."
msgstr "不。再见。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Not yet."
msgstr "还没呢。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Nothing."
msgstr "没什么。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid ""
"I do need your help about a thing, but you should talk to our researcher "
"about this first."
msgstr "我确实有件事需要你帮忙，但你应该先和我们的研究员谈谈这个。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I will."
msgstr "我会的。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid ""
"Good. Since I don't have any problems at all, you should check others of "
"their needs."
msgstr "很好。既然我没有任何问题，你应该去检查其他人的需求。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Not until we get back to the others."
msgstr "等我们回到其他人那里再说。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "Will do."
msgstr "会的。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "What is this place?"
msgstr "这是什么地方？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "What are you doing?"
msgstr "你在做什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr "你是谁？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Bye."
msgstr "再见。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid ""
"Currently this building is military outpost. M1 might give you more specific"
" information."
msgstr "目前这栋建筑是军事前哨站。M1可能会给你更具体的信息。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "Okay…"
msgstr "好吧……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "I just clean here. Go talk with M1."
msgstr "我只是在这里打扫。去和M1谈谈吧。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "Will do. Bye."
msgstr "会的。再见。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "I'm security of this area. I serving under Sgt M1."
msgstr "我是这个区域的安全人员。我在M1中士手下服务。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "I see."
msgstr "我明白了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Great job, survivor. I never expect an outsider help us with our dilemma, "
"yet here you are."
msgstr "干得好，幸存者。我从没指望一个外来者能帮我们解决困境，但你却做到了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "You better get going."
msgstr "你最好赶紧出发。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr "是什么事？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "You are not authorized to this area."
msgstr "你无权进入这个区域。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "We need to go."
msgstr "我们得走了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Yeah, and I want to know more about your plans."
msgstr "是的，而且我想了解更多关于你们的计划。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "The guard told me you need assistance."
msgstr "守卫告诉我你需要帮助。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "What's your plan?"
msgstr "你有什么计划？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "We've clear the enigma chamber."
msgstr "我们已经清理了谜团室。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Anything else I can do?"
msgstr "还有其他我能做的吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "How's the search for specimen?"
msgstr "样本搜寻进展如何？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Bye then..."
msgstr "那就再见了……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "I am."
msgstr "我是。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "I know. Just lead us all to that chamber."
msgstr "我知道。只需带领我们所有人去那个房间。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "好的。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Yes, since you've proven yourself worthy for our plans, I'll be glad if you "
"help me with this rather odd request."
msgstr "是的，既然你已证明自己配得上我们的计划，如果你能帮我处理这个相当奇怪的请求，我会很高兴。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Since you've proven yourself worthy for our future plans, I'll be glad if "
"you help me with this rather odd request."
msgstr "既然你已证明自己配得上我们未来的计划，如果你能帮我处理这个相当奇怪的请求，我会很高兴。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Tell me."
msgstr "告诉我。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"But first, let me tell you a subtle understanding on our facility. There are"
" a total of 3 specimen variants: the failed, BOW and enigma, each in their "
"respective rooms."
msgstr "但首先，让我告诉你对我们设施的简要了解。总共有3种样本变体：失败型、BOW型和谜团型，各自位于相应的房间。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Failed? BOW? Enigma? What are those?"
msgstr "失败型？BOW型？谜团型？那些是什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Just describe what needs to be done."
msgstr "只需描述需要做什么。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Failed specimens are the results of unsuccessful mutations, otherwise they "
"are called BOWs. Enigmas, on the other hand, were formed using potent "
"mutagens."
msgstr "失败样本是突变不成功的产物，否则它们被称为BOW。而谜团型则是使用强效诱变剂形成的。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "So what should I do?"
msgstr "那么我该做什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Clear out the enigma chamber. That room were locked down due to extremely "
"anomalous threats, and you'll need authorization from someone to open it up."
" If you're ready, talk to the guard about this."
msgstr "清理谜团室。那个房间因极端异常威胁而被封锁，你需要获得某人的授权才能打开它。如果你准备好了，就和守卫谈谈这件事。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay. I will go now"
msgstr "好的。我现在就去。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Excellent. Have you found anything of interest?"
msgstr "很好。你发现什么有趣的东西了吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Nope."
msgstr "不。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"If you notice anything strange, just ask me and I'll tell everything I know "
"about that."
msgstr "如果你注意到任何奇怪的事情，尽管问我，我会告诉你我所知道的一切。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay. Bye."
msgstr "好的。再见。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Well, I'm curious about a mysterious, wandering specimen. Its the result of "
"our recent experiment using a highly unstable mutagen who, I believe, takes "
"form of a human."
msgstr "嗯，我对一个神秘的、游荡的样本很好奇。它是我们最近使用一种高度不稳定的诱变剂进行实验的结果，我相信它以人类的形式存在。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "What do you from it?"
msgstr "你想从它那里得到什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Unlike other enigmas, its genetic structure is of unknown form, and I need a"
" sample from it for deeper understanding of this otherworldly creature."
msgstr "与其他谜团不同，它的遗传结构形式未知，我需要从它那里获取样本，以更深入地理解这种异界生物。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "So where can I find it?"
msgstr "那么我在哪里能找到它？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"That's not necessary, as while you were dealing with the enigma chamber, "
"I've sent a scout drone to search for that specimen using a tracker device, "
"and it may take a while for its report."
msgstr "那没必要，因为在你处理谜团密室时，我已经派出一架侦察无人机，使用追踪设备搜索那个样本，它的报告可能需要一段时间。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay... I'll wait for it."
msgstr "好的……我会等待。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "The drone's still on the search..."
msgstr "无人机仍在搜索中……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr "好吧……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "The drone has revealed the location of our target."
msgstr "无人机已经揭示了目标的位置。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay, what should I do?"
msgstr "好的，我该做什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "… oh… yes?"
msgstr "……哦……是的？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "What are you working on here?"
msgstr "你在这里做什么工作？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "So, this is your lab?"
msgstr "那么，这是你的实验室？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "I'm working on the Flesh. Most of the time."
msgstr "我在研究血肉。大部分时间都是。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "The flesh? So you are kind of a doctor?"
msgstr "血肉？所以你算是医生？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"Oh not exactly, rather scientist. The Flesh is organic flesh-like matter "
"designed for wide variety of purposes. In short, it can be grown into "
"various tissues with various structure. It can create muscles, bones, "
"organs, glands, even whole self sufficient micro and macro organisms."
msgstr ""
"哦，不完全是，更准确说是科学家。血肉是一种有机的、类似肉体的物质，设计用于多种目的。简而言之，它可以生长成具有各种结构的组织。它能创造肌肉、骨骼、器官、腺体，甚至整个自给自足的微观和宏观生物体。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"My lab and my home. I created this lab long time ago when I decided to do "
"something useful. I believed that research on stem cells, cultured meat and "
"synthetic organs would solve many problems. "
msgstr "我的实验室和我的家。很久以前，当我决定做些有用的事情时，我创建了这个实验室。我相信对干细胞、培养肉和合成器官的研究会解决许多问题。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "That sounds interesting, what kind of problems you had on mind?"
msgstr "听起来很有趣，你当时想到了哪些问题？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "You created this whole lab yourself?"
msgstr "这整个实验室都是你自己建造的？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"Well nothing too specific in particular. Back then, goal of my research was "
"anything from efficient edible meat production, growing organs for "
"transplatology, various therapies with stem cells and most importantly "
"getting funds for my living and playing with life."
msgstr ""
"其实也没什么特别具体的方向。那时候，我的研究目标五花八门，从高效食用肉生产、为移植学培育器官、各种干细胞疗法，最重要的是获取维持生活和玩弄生命的资金。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"Oh yes, it took many years to gather funds, collect gear and set it all up "
"down here. Through years of my research I was leading various projects and "
"collected quite a lot of funds. Later on I had to tightly lock this place "
"and move permanently to other facility."
msgstr ""
"哦，是的，我花了好多年才筹集资金、收集设备，并把这里的一切都布置妥当。多年的研究里，我主导了各种项目，积累了相当可观的资金。后来我不得不把这里严密封锁，永久转移到其他设施去。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "Quite remarkable achievement, what forced you to move from here?"
msgstr "真是了不起的成就，是什么迫使你从这里搬走的？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"I could either move with my research to more secured facility or loose "
"control over my research on the Flesh. I wasn't happy by that, boss hovering"
" over my shoulder, evaluating my work was hard to accept. Though considering"
" how it all turned out I'm glad they forced me back then."
msgstr ""
"我当时要么带着研究搬到更安全的设施，要么就得失去对“血肉”研究的控制。我对此并不满意，老板在背后盯着，评估我的工作，这很难接受。不过考虑到后来发生的一切，我很庆幸他们当时逼我搬走了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "So the work under someone wasn't so bad?"
msgstr "所以，在别人手下工作也没那么糟？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"Oh it was, it's just that when everything went to hell, we had a little "
"accident there. Instead of me having little accident here."
msgstr "哦，其实很糟，只是当一切都乱套时，我们在那边出了点小事故。而不是我在这里出点小事故。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "I see…"
msgstr "我明白了……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "What do you need, survivor?"
msgstr "你需要什么，幸存者？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "You need something?"
msgstr "你需要什么吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Now that we're here, we won't be bothered by those shambling maneaters... "
"for now."
msgstr "既然我们在这里，暂时不会被那些蹒跚的食人者打扰了……目前是这样。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "No, this is not the BOW chamber..."
msgstr "不，这不是BOW实验室……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Perhaps I've told you everything I know..."
msgstr "也许我已经把我知道的都告诉你了……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "You need to know more information?"
msgstr "你需要了解更多信息吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"A survivor? What are you doing here despite the raging chaos?\n"
"Anyway, you'll be safe in here."
msgstr ""
"一个幸存者？尽管外面一片混乱，你在这里做什么？\n"
"不管怎样，你在这里会很安全。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "So what are your future plans?"
msgstr "那你未来的计划是什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'm ready to push forward."
msgstr "我准备好继续前进了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'd like to know more about the secronom project."
msgstr "我想了解更多关于secronom项目的信息。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Is there anything I can do to help?"
msgstr "有什么我能帮忙的吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'm ready for the job."
msgstr "我准备好接受任务了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "About the repairs..."
msgstr "关于修理的事……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'm a researcher."
msgstr "我是一名研究员。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Of what exactly?"
msgstr "具体研究什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Its not important, but if you wish to know, I don't mind ... since "
"everything's messed up already."
msgstr "这不重要，但如果你想知道，我不介意……反正一切都乱套了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Then tell me your secrets."
msgstr "那就告诉我你的秘密吧。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Lets talk about that later."
msgstr "我们晚点再谈这个。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"... Its the secronom project, a project that involves human augmentation "
"using animal and alien genetics."
msgstr "……是塞克洛诺姆计划，一个利用动物和外星基因进行人体强化的项目。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "And what's the purpose of the secronom project?"
msgstr "塞克洛诺姆项目的目的是什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Human augmentation?"
msgstr "人体强化？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "What about genetics?"
msgstr "那基因方面呢？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I guess I've asked everything..."
msgstr "我想我已经问完所有问题了……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"For military, yet I'm not sure if there's beyond that case. I don't know "
"what it is, but the ones who can answer that are not in here anymore."
msgstr "为了军事用途，但我不确定是否还有其他目的。我不知道具体是什么，但能回答这个问题的人已经不在这里了。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"You heard it. The government permits this project to perform human "
"experimentation. Don't worry, the subjects here are outlaws of the society."
msgstr "你听到了。政府允许这个项目进行人体实验。别担心，这里的实验对象都是社会上的不法之徒。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "And what's the purpose of secronom?"
msgstr "那塞克洛诺姆的目的是什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "... but they didn't deserve this."
msgstr "……但他们不该遭受这些。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"We've extracted the genes of an animal, then mixed with a catalyst. The "
"catalyst is a classified object, so I can't tell you what it is."
msgstr "我们提取了动物的基因，然后与催化剂混合。催化剂是机密物品，所以我不能告诉你它是什么。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"This is the secronom bunker, built solely as our last option for survival."
msgstr "这里是塞克洛诺姆地堡，是作为我们最后的生存选择而建造的。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "So why won't you escape this place?"
msgstr "那你为什么不逃离这个地方？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Why is it connected to the lab?"
msgstr "为什么它与实验室相连？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Well? What have you earned for doing those?"
msgstr "那么？你做这些得到了什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"I know escaping is our best option, but what lies beyond the wastelands is "
"our main reason why we shouldn't travel."
msgstr "我知道逃离是最好的选择，但废土之外的存在正是我们不应远行的主要原因。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "So why is it connected to the lab?"
msgstr "那它为什么与实验室相连？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "(pussies)"
msgstr "（胆小鬼）"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"That's because we work in there, and performing scientific experiments and "
"discovering newfound technologies is our foundation."
msgstr "因为我们在那里工作，进行科学实验和发现新技术是我们的根基。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Why won't you escape this place?"
msgstr "你为什么不逃离这个地方？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Regrets. I know you have encountered those ugly bastards, but they are the "
"result of our experiments. And the tech? All of them are incomplete."
msgstr "遗憾。我知道你遇到过那些丑陋的混蛋，但他们是实验的产物。而那些技术？全都未完成。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "... So, is there anything else I need to know about the lab?"
msgstr "……那么，关于实验室还有什么我需要知道的吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "That's unfortunate, but there's nothing I can do."
msgstr "这很不幸，但我无能为力。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Well, if you're interested, I can tell you one thing... Deep below this "
"facility is a weapon of mass destruction, created for military \"use\"."
msgstr "好吧，如果你感兴趣，我可以告诉你一件事……这个设施深处有一件大规模杀伤性武器，是为军事“用途”而造的。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Thanks for the info, I guess..."
msgstr "多谢告知，我想……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "My plan is a bit risky, and I'll need you to guide us all."
msgstr "我的计划有点冒险，需要你来引导我们所有人。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'm in for that!"
msgstr "我加入！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Maybe later."
msgstr "也许晚点再说。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Now, let's plow through the horde!"
msgstr "现在，让我们杀出一条血路！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Good. We need you to help us take over the BOW's chamber. With that, we can "
"once again perform scientific experiments solely for our survival."
msgstr "很好。我们需要你帮忙接管BOW的舱室。这样我们就能再次进行科学实验，只为我们自己的生存。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Lets go!"
msgstr "出发吧！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "... later, I need to gear up."
msgstr "……稍等，我得准备装备。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'll lead the way!"
msgstr "我来带路！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"This is science, you see? You may think we're the gruesome ones, but what we want is to open up new discoveries for us all. Yes, we messed up, but we're still here, struggling and helping each other to survive this nightmare.\n"
"I can't change your opinion towards us, but if you want to know more about the secronom project, talk to our researcher."
msgstr ""
"这就是科学，明白吗？你可能觉得我们很可怕，但我们想要的是为所有人开辟新的发现。是的，我们搞砸了，但我们还在这里，挣扎着互相帮助，在这场噩梦中求生。\n"
"我无法改变你对我们的看法，但如果你想了解更多关于secronom项目的信息，去和我们的研究员谈谈。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I see, you're curious about our \"unexpecting\" creations..."
msgstr "我明白了，你对我们的“意外”造物很好奇……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "What's on your mind?"
msgstr "你在想什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Are those mutants in the city were the result of secronom project?"
msgstr "城市里的那些突变体是塞克诺姆项目的产物吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Are there some other threats this project has created that I need to be "
"aware of?"
msgstr "这个项目还制造了其他我需要警惕的威胁吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "...."
msgstr "……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"What? That can't be good...\n"
"You know, secronom has an extreme potency of alteration once it comes in contact with a viable victim. If mixed with the catalyst, this will turn one's body into an adaptive living weapon, but that doesn't always end to the same result."
msgstr ""
"什么？那可不太妙……\n"
"要知道，塞克诺姆一旦接触合适的受害者，就会展现出极强的改造能力。如果与催化剂混合，它能把人的身体变成适应性活体武器，但结果并不总是相同。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "So how did it spread?"
msgstr "那它是怎么传播的？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"It is an unstable pathogen - evolving more by time, and due to the outbreak,"
" this facility falls into chaos; everyone panics, and got their body ripped "
"to shred. Secronom were doomed to spread throughout the world in that "
"incident."
msgstr ""
"这是一种不稳定的病原体——随时间推移不断进化，而由于那次爆发，设施陷入混乱；人人恐慌，身体被撕成碎片。塞克诺姆在那次事件中注定要蔓延至全世界。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Actually, there are 3 that we've discovered so far and maybe there's more to"
" appear."
msgstr "实际上，我们目前发现了3种，可能还有更多会出现。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Where are they? And what do you mean by \"discovered\"?"
msgstr "它们在哪里？你说的“发现”是什么意思？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Those mutants think different than a zombified egghead, and probably they're in the woods, having a stroll.\n"
"We discovered them by applying a super concentrated type of mutagen into each of our subjects, and the results, few of them transformed into these abominations, while the rest died... which is unfortunate, as our team thought their masculine body can handle such potential power."
msgstr ""
"那些突变体的思维方式与僵尸化的书呆子不同，它们可能在树林里闲逛。\n"
"我们通过向每个实验对象注射超浓缩型诱变剂发现了它们，结果少数变成了这些怪物，其余的则死了……这很不幸，因为我们团队原以为他们强健的体魄能承受这种潜在力量。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Well, now I know your team did an inhumane act..."
msgstr "好吧，现在我知道你的团队做了不人道的事……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"There is something I want to work on for our defenses, but they require time"
" and vast amounts of materials for the process."
msgstr "我想为我们的防御工事做点东西，但这需要时间和大量材料。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Defenses? You mean turrets?"
msgstr "防御工事？你是指炮塔吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Take your time while you gather them."
msgstr "收集材料时请慢慢来。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Yes, the autonomous turrets that you saw on the bunker is what I want to "
"acquire. Do you accept my request?"
msgstr "是的，你在掩体看到的自动炮塔就是我想要获取的。你接受我的请求吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "是的。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'll do it later."
msgstr "我稍后再做。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I'm currently working on repairs..."
msgstr "我正在修理中……"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "What do you want to repair?"
msgstr "你想修理什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "Let me check the progress of SDP-L1 turret's repair."
msgstr "让我检查一下SDP-L1炮塔的修理进度。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "SDP-L1 turret."
msgstr "SDP-L1炮塔。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I'll check them later."
msgstr "我稍后再检查它们。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I got nothing."
msgstr "我没什么可说的。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid ""
"It is done. I modified the turret and made it cheaper in power usage, with a"
" built-in storage battery."
msgstr "完成了。我改装了炮塔，降低了它的能耗，还加装了内置蓄电池。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I'll take it!"
msgstr "我要了！"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I need more time to fully repair the turret."
msgstr "我需要更多时间来彻底修复炮塔。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid ""
"To repair the SDP-L1 turret, I need the following resources:\n"
"\n"
"4 chunks of steel\n"
"18 scrap metals\n"
"9 electronic scraps\n"
"9 power converters\n"
"5 copper wires\n"
"\n"
"It takes more than an hour to complete the process."
msgstr ""
"要修复SDP-L1炮塔，我需要以下资源：\n"
"\n"
"4块钢锭\n"
"18块废金属\n"
"9个电子废料\n"
"9个电源转换器\n"
"5根铜线\n"
"\n"
"整个过程需要一个多小时。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "[REPAIR]"
msgstr "[修复]"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "Perform the repair later."
msgstr "稍后再进行修复。"

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I need more resources."
msgstr "我需要更多资源。"

#. ~ Please leave anything in <angle brackets> unchanged.
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_flags.json
msgid ""
"This gear has been coated in bio-organic mesh, increasing its "
"<good>protection</good>."
msgstr "这件装备已涂覆生物有机网层，提升了其<good>防护性</good>。"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Experimental"
msgstr "实验性"

#. ~ Mutation class: Experimental mutagen_message
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You feel so strange."
msgstr "你感觉非常奇怪。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Experimental iv_message
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You inject yoursel-arRGH!"
msgstr "你给自己注射——啊！"

#. ~ Mutation class: Experimental iv_sleep_message
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You were knocked unconscious and spasm to the ground."
msgstr "你被击昏，痉挛倒地。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Experimental iv_sound_message
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "yourself scream in agony!"
msgstr "你自己在痛苦中尖叫！"

#. ~ Mutation class: Experimental Male memorial messsage
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "Burst out of humanity."
msgstr "人性崩坏。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Experimental Female memorial messsage
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "Burst out of humanity."
msgstr "人性崩坏。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Mutant"
msgstr "突变体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mutant'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You're still bothered why'd you choose this mess..."
msgstr "你仍在困惑为何选择这团糟……"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "experimental mutagen"
msgid_plural "experimental mutagens"
msgstr[0] "实验性突变剂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'experimental mutagen'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Mutagen developed by the secronom team. Unstable."
msgstr "由secronom团队研发的突变剂。不稳定。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "experimental serum"
msgid_plural "experimental serums"
msgstr[0] "实验性血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'experimental serum'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Super-concentrated mutagen developed by the secronom team. Highly unstable. "
msgstr "由secronom团队研发的超浓缩突变剂。极不稳定。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Tendrils"
msgstr "触须"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tendrils'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your arms were replaced by a pair of tough, skinny tendrils. Good for "
"combat, but it's stiff and prevents you from wearing gloves."
msgstr "你的双臂被一对坚韧而细长的触须所取代。这有利于战斗，但触须僵硬，让你无法佩戴手套。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You slap %s with your tendrils"
msgstr "你用触须拍击了%s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "%1$s strikes %2$s with their tendrils"
msgstr "%1$s用他们的触须攻击了%2$s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Thick Tendrils"
msgstr "粗壮触须"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Thick Tendrils'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"You've got a pair of large, thick tendrils sprouting from your arms. They "
"decreases your dex by 2, but impacts more damage and has increased bash "
"resistance."
msgstr "你的双臂长出了一对又大又粗的触须。它们使你的敏捷降低2点，但能造成更多伤害，并提高了钝击抗性。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You slap %s with your thick tendrils"
msgstr "你用粗壮的触须拍击了%s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "%1$s strikes %2$s with their thick tendrils"
msgstr "%1$s用他们粗壮的触须攻击了%2$s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Tendricles"
msgstr "触须丛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tendricles'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your whole body has small wriggly tentacle outgrowths, while your tendril "
"pairs became shorter in length, increasing dex by 1 and decreasing their "
"encumbrance and impact damage. The outgrowths are tough, providing 1 bash "
"resistance to all body parts, yet increases their encumbrance by 5 and "
"becomes much more uncomfortable when wearing tight clothes."
msgstr ""
"你的全身长出了细小的蠕动触须状增生，同时你的成对触须长度变短，这使敏捷增加1点，并降低了它们的累赘度和冲击伤害。这些增生很坚韧，为所有身体部位提供1点钝击抗性，但会使累赘度增加5点，并且在穿着紧身衣物时变得非常不适。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You pierced %s with your tendrils"
msgstr "你用触须刺穿了%s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "%1$s pierces %2$s with their tendrils"
msgstr "%1$s用他们的触须刺穿了%2$s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Core - Tendril"
msgstr "核心 - 触须"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core - Tendril'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your tendrils limbs have become tougher, stronger and darker in hue due to "
"prolonged mutations. Permanently increases your strength by 2, bash damage "
"by 4 and their physical resistance by 4."
msgstr "由于长期的突变，你的触须肢体变得更坚韧、更强壮，色泽也更深沉。永久增加你的力量2点，钝击伤害4点，以及物理抗性4点。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core - Tendril'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"One of your tendril limbs have swollen a bit, and faintly pulsates in "
"velvety hue. If activated, this tendril hardens, extends and becomes a "
"special whip-like weapon for a few turns."
msgstr "你的一条触须肢体略微肿胀，并以天鹅绒般的色泽微弱地搏动着。如果激活，这条触须会硬化、延伸，并在数回合内变成一种特殊的鞭状武器。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Bone Blade"
msgstr "骨刃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bone Blade'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your left hand has lost its flesh, revealing only a stout bone blade. It "
"prevents you from wearing gloves nor handling anything with, but has great "
"resistance against physical damage plus it packs a wallop."
msgstr "你的左手失去了血肉，只剩下一把粗壮的骨刃。它让你无法佩戴手套或用手处理任何物品，但对物理伤害有很强的抗性，并且威力巨大。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Sharpened Bone Blade"
msgstr "锋锐骨刃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sharpened Bone Blade'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your bone blade became lighter, thinner and has a sharpened edge, like that "
"of a sword. Instead of impact damage, it cuts through flesh with ease."
msgstr "你的骨刃变得更轻、更薄，并且拥有像剑一样锋利的刃口。它不再造成冲击伤害，而是能轻易地切割血肉。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Serrated Bone Blade"
msgstr "锯齿骨刃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Serrated Bone Blade'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your bone blade has greatly altered, forming irregular bone outgrowths all "
"around the surface. It is heavier and very unpleasant to the sight, but "
"beneficial for both defense and offense."
msgstr "你的骨刃发生了巨大的变化，表面形成了不规则的骨质增生。它更重且外观非常令人不适，但对防御和进攻都有益处。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Core - Blade"
msgstr "核心 - 刀刃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core - Blade'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your blade has been engulfed by veins, pulsating in sync with your beats. It"
" glows brighter whenever you take damage from a foe. Receiving damage from "
"an enemy attack increases your combat abilities for a short period of time."
msgstr "你的刀刃已被血管吞噬，随着你的心跳同步搏动。每当你受到敌人伤害时，它会发出更明亮的光芒。受到敌人攻击伤害会在短时间内提升你的战斗能力。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core - Blade'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your blade were overwhelmed by flesh strands, throbbing at a constant rate. "
"These strands react from enemy attacks, which causes them to spread and "
"cover your extremities. Whenever you take damage from a foe, your chance of "
"blocking their attacks will increase for a few moments, but also decreases "
"your mobility and attack speed."
msgstr ""
"你的刀刃被肉丝覆盖，以恒定速率悸动。这些肉丝会对敌人攻击产生反应，导致它们扩散并覆盖你的四肢。每当你受到敌人伤害时，你格挡其攻击的几率会短暂提升，但也会降低你的移动速度和攻击速度。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Irregular Bone Outgrowths"
msgstr "不规则骨刺增生"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Irregular Bone Outgrowths'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Sharp bones protrude through your skin, extending at random angles. In "
"exchange of mobility and 10 encumbrance to all body parts, they greatly "
"protect you from harm."
msgstr "尖锐的骨头刺穿你的皮肤，以随机角度延伸。以牺牲移动性和所有身体部位增加10点负重为代价，它们极大地保护你免受伤害。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Plated Bone Outgrowths"
msgstr "板状骨刺增生"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Plated Bone Outgrowths'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"The bone outgrowths has extended further, and their angles has slightly "
"adjusted. Underneath them are irregular bone plates that spread over your "
"skin, expanding their coverage. Significantly improves your defensive "
"capabilities, however, they harshly affect your mobility and increases "
"encumbrance by 15 caused by additional weight."
msgstr ""
"骨刺增生进一步延伸，其角度略有调整。下方是不规则的骨板，在你的皮肤上蔓延，扩大了覆盖范围。显著提升你的防御能力，但会严重影响移动性，并因额外重量增加15点负重。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Bone Cuirass"
msgstr "骨制胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bone Cuirass'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your bone outgrowths became an external layer of armor, which fits and "
"excels at protecting your body while severely reducing the length of the "
"spikes. The spikes have adjusted enough to reduce movement penalties and "
"encumbrance to 8, but permanently disables the ability to pierce the "
"attackers."
msgstr ""
"你的骨刺增生形成了一层外部护甲，贴合身体并擅长防护，同时大幅缩短了尖刺长度。尖刺经过调整，将移动惩罚和负重降低至8点，但永久失去了刺穿攻击者的能力。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Massive Bone Outgrowths"
msgstr "巨型骨刺增生"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Massive Bone Outgrowths'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your bone outgrowths have altered to a great extent - bone plates have "
"swollen and the spikes grew unnecessary sets of smaller variations. Aside "
"from its significantly improved defense that adds 12 physical resistance to "
"all body parts, its weight and thickness are a hassle, permanently "
"increasing encumbrance by 20 and a greatly reduced mobility."
msgstr ""
"你的骨刺增生发生了巨大改变——骨板肿胀，尖刺生长出多余的小型变体。除了显著提升防御，为所有身体部位增加12点物理抗性外，其重量和厚度成为负担，永久增加20点负重并大幅降低移动性。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Arachnid Limbs"
msgstr "蛛形肢体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Arachnid Limbs'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"You grew 2 additional pairs of arms sticking out from the sides of your "
"torso close to the abdominal part. They seem to function as duplicates of "
"normal ones, gaining 1 permanent dex and making them beneficial for "
"crafting, combat and vaulting through objects, but increases torsal "
"encumbrance by 10 which triples when you wear a tight clothing."
msgstr ""
"你从躯干侧面靠近腹部的位置长出了两对额外的手臂。它们似乎能像正常手臂一样运作，永久增加1点敏捷，对制作、战斗和翻越物体有益，但增加躯干负重10点，穿着紧身衣物时该效果会变为三倍。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Augmented Arachnid Limbs"
msgstr "强化蛛形肢体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Augmented Arachnid Limbs'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your additional limbs have become more responsive, which eases your control "
"over them. They permanently increases your dex by 2 and slightly improving "
"its basic modifiers."
msgstr "你的额外肢体变得更加灵敏，便于你控制它们。它们永久增加2点敏捷，并略微提升基础修正值。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Deformed Arachnid Limbs"
msgstr "畸形蛛形肢体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Deformed Arachnid Limbs'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your extra limbs became twisted and malformed, which slightly affects the "
"movements of your arms. They removed your permanent dex, increased your "
"torsal encumbrance by 15 and a drastic reduction to its basic modifiers."
msgstr "你的额外肢体变得扭曲畸形，略微影响手臂动作。它们移除了你的永久敏捷加成，增加躯干负重15点，并大幅降低基础修正值。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Superior Arachnid Limbs"
msgstr "卓越蛛形肢体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Superior Arachnid Limbs'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Further mutations has caused your limbs to unify with your cerebral cortex, "
"accepting them as part of your body. With full control over them, they "
"permanently increases your dex by 3 and significantly improves the basic "
"modifiers."
msgstr "进一步的突变使你的肢体与大脑皮层融合，被身体完全接纳。在完全控制下，它们永久增加3点敏捷，并显著提升基础修正值。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Lushen Tongue"
msgstr "繁茂之舌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lushen Tongue'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue have become long and slender that stretches and retracts at your"
" will. It somewhat helps you in sensing scents and movements."
msgstr "你的舌头变得细长，能随你心意伸缩。这在一定程度上帮助你感知气味和动静。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You lick %s"
msgstr "你舔了舔%s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "%1$s licks %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s舔了舔%2$s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Malformed Tongue"
msgstr "畸形舌头"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Malformed Tongue'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue has deformed into a large, unpleasant tendril-like flesh strand."
" It greatly hampers your breathing, reducing your stamina by 30% and is "
"useless when it comes to sensing nearby creatures."
msgstr "你的舌头已变形为一条粗大、令人不适的触手状肉条。它严重妨碍你的呼吸，使耐力降低30%，且在感知附近生物方面毫无用处。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Callous Tongue"
msgstr "硬茧舌头"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Callous Tongue'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"From prolonged alteration, your tongue have sightly become thicker and "
"harder, yet still retains its flexibility."
msgstr "由于长期变异，你的舌头略微变厚变硬，但仍保持其柔韧性。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Tongue Hypertrophy"
msgstr "舌头肥大"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tongue Hypertrophy'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue has hardened and swollen a bit. You find conversations tricky "
"and its larger scale has greatly reduced their sensing capability, yet their"
" resistance helps alot in blocking incoming damage."
msgstr "你的舌头变硬并略微肿胀。你发现交谈变得困难，其增大的尺寸极大降低了感知能力，但其增强的抵抗力在抵挡来袭伤害时大有帮助。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Succulent Tongue"
msgstr "多汁舌头"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Succulent Tongue'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue has slightly become thinner and longer, which further improves "
"your senses and combat capabilities."
msgstr "你的舌头变得更细更长，进一步提升了你的感知能力和战斗效能。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Tongue Lasher"
msgstr "鞭舌者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tongue Lasher'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Due to further alteration, your tongue have become broader and has developed"
" a set of retractable bony blades on either sides of its surface. Despite "
"its significant improvements on senses and offensive capabilities, your "
"conversations with other people also becomes much more difficult to "
"handle... but find it great for terrorizing."
msgstr ""
"由于进一步变异，你的舌头变得更宽，并在其表面两侧长出了一组可伸缩的骨刃。尽管它在感知和攻击能力上显著提升，但与他人的交谈也变得难以进行……不过用来恐吓倒是效果绝佳。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You lashed %s with your tongue"
msgstr "你用舌头鞭打了%s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "%1$s lashes %2$s with their tongue"
msgstr "%1$s用舌头鞭打了%2$s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Core - Licker"
msgstr "核心 - 舔食者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core - Licker'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your tongue secretes concentrated saliva whenever it gets stretched. This "
"allows your lick attacks to enlow the target in combat."
msgstr "你的舌头在伸展时会分泌浓缩唾液。这使你的舔舐攻击能在战斗中削弱目标。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core - Licker'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"The blades on your tongue were sharpened and is pulsating in dark, velvety "
"streaks. This greatly improves the damage of lick attacks, as well as its "
"potency in combat."
msgstr "你舌头上的骨刃变得锋利，并脉动着暗色天鹅绒般的纹路。这极大提升了舔舐攻击的伤害及其在战斗中的效力。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Shoulder Bumps"
msgstr "肩部隆起"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shoulder Bumps'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You've got a bumps on both of your shoulder joints."
msgstr "你的双肩关节处出现了隆起。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Membranous Wings"
msgstr "膜状翅膀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Membranous Wings'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"You've got wing-like appendages sprouting on your shoulder joints stretching"
" down to your pelvis. The wing is composed of muscle tissues and fiber "
"webbings, with each ends tipped with a sharp, bony blade appendixes. They "
"might be encumbering and heavy, but their strong build provides +2 strength."
msgstr ""
"你的肩关节处长出了翅膀状的附肢，一直延伸到骨盆。翅膀由肌肉组织和纤维网构成，末端带有尖锐的骨刃附肢。它们可能笨重且累赘，但其坚固的结构提供了+2力量。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You rake %s"
msgstr "你抓挠%s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "%1$s rakes %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s抓挠%2$s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Skeletal Wings"
msgstr "骨骼翅膀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Skeletal Wings'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Protruding from your shoulder is a thin, flexible pair of endoskeletal "
"wings. Though bulky and encumbering, they can be used to balance your "
"movements, handling heavy stuff and shredding anyone you dislike."
msgstr "从你的肩膀伸出一对纤细灵活的内骨骼翅膀。虽然笨重且累赘，但它们可以用来平衡你的动作，处理重物，并撕碎任何你不喜欢的人。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You thrust you wings towards %s"
msgstr "你将翅膀刺向%s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "%1$s thrusts their wings %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s将翅膀刺向%2$s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Fleshed Mantle"
msgstr "肉膜披风"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fleshed Mantle'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"You've grown a mass of flabby flesh from your shoulders to the back of your "
"body. Aside from being able to deflect physical harm, it severely hampers "
"your movements and actions that requires finesse."
msgstr "你的肩膀到背部生长出一大块松弛的肉膜。除了能够偏转物理伤害外，它严重妨碍了你的移动和需要精细操作的动作。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You slam %s with your mantle"
msgstr "你用披风猛击%s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "%1$s slams %2$s with their mantle"
msgstr "%1$s用披风猛击%2$s"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Tumors"
msgstr "肿瘤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tumors'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You have small head bumps scattered underneath your scalp."
msgstr "你的头皮下散布着一些小肿块。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Eyegrowths"
msgstr "眼芽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Eyegrowths'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"You have several eyesprouts scattered throughout your hair, and they are "
"sometimes painful when covered by a headgear. Provides additional vision "
"bonuses and increases your perception by 3, but increases head encumbrance "
"by 20."
msgstr "你的头发中散布着几个眼芽，戴头饰时有时会感到疼痛。提供额外的视觉加成，感知增加3，但头部负重增加20。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Writhing Proboscides"
msgstr "扭动口器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Writhing Proboscides'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"You've got a few, slender proboscides on your head. They twitch "
"occasionally, and involuntarily, increasing head encumbrance by 25.  If "
"conditions are met, they can suck the lifeforce out of your victim... only "
"if they're alive."
msgstr "你的头上有几个细长的口器。它们偶尔会不自主地抽动，使头部负重增加25。如果条件满足，它们可以从受害者身上吸取生命力……前提是对方还活着。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Who needs veggy?"
msgstr "谁还需要蔬菜？"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Debug Hivemind"
msgstr "调试蜂巢思维"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Debug Hivemind'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "How's in charge now?!"
msgstr "现在谁负责？！"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Flesh Hivemind"
msgstr "血肉蜂巢思维"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flesh Hivemind'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "You might be immobile, but you have the power to dominate the world!"
msgstr "你或许无法移动，但你有力量主宰世界！"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Flesh Hivemind - Active"
msgstr "血肉蜂巢思维 - 活跃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flesh Hivemind - Active'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your tentacles has detached from the ground! This causes you to take damage "
"until you reattach to a terrain."
msgstr "你的触手已从地面脱离！这会导致你受到伤害，直到你重新附着到地形上。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Unstable Hivemind"
msgstr "不稳定蜂巢思维"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Unstable Hivemind'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Your body slowly melts away!"
msgstr "你的身体正逐渐融化！"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Infectious Tendrils"
msgstr "感染触须"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Infectious Tendrils'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
